        <h3>Major Chris Green</h3>
        <p>
          Chris Green will serve as the strength and conditioning coach for the
          team this year.  This is his second year with the team and he is
          currently a graduate student at Stanford in the Management Science
          and Engineering.  Chris has spent the last 10 years as an officer in
          the United States Army with 5 tours to Iraq/Afghanistan.  Chris
          played college lacrosse at the United States Military Academy at West
          Point.
        </p>
